{"tid":1357252,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝備撚] 我想買個頭盔番工同打War Game 求介紹","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:39:58.000Z","uid":8005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76c747b52e38a3b601637e5d722a57517b1ea38a","tid":1357252,"uid":8005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:31:15.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見就黎秋天可以打War game, 依家又開始興帶頭盔番工翻工，想揾番一套頭盔，面罩同眼鏡可以一齊帶 , 一雞幾咪<br />\n<br />\n眼鏡其實我已經買左Pyramex I-Force Glasses (Around HKD 2xx) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71MBXxSZS4L._UX679_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F71MBXxSZS4L._UX679_.jpg&h=86ad288a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個鏡冇咩特別，係特別多狗用, 聽聞飛狗隊都係用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/60761673_2160718034046557_1853880641423147008_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQlXQYxDt0wlb7qYE3Cr9MCX16FcjTnkPKzb4LhDQQAjmjs-_W-QyDEz08kcICdEq8g&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=725724795ca9c0042ac216f47cdc8a90&amp;oe=5DAE4916\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F60761673_2160718034046557_1853880641423147008_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQlXQYxDt0wlb7qYE3Cr9MCX16FcjTnkPKzb4LhDQQAjmjs-_W-QyDEz08kcICdEq8g%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D725724795ca9c0042ac216f47cdc8a90%26oe%3D5DAE4916&h=be9b9b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁重點黎啦! 到個頭盔! 我心目中係想要依種<br />\n<img src=\"https://go3.imgsmail.ru/imgpreview?key=5c3e991bfdc98368&amp;mb=storage\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgo3.imgsmail.ru%2Fimgpreview%3Fkey%3D5c3e991bfdc98368%26mb%3Dstorage&h=96c5e7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但怕比BB 彈彈到面仔，所以想睇埋個貼面d 既Mask, 因為打War game 要睇紅點鏡<br />\n個Mask 想類似依種可以cover 多少少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://shoplineimg.com/5a4b0aba080f06ac7800059d/5a56e4f1d4e39567350019bf/800x.webp?source_format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshoplineimg.com%2F5a4b0aba080f06ac7800059d%2F5a56e4f1d4e39567350019bf%2F800x.webp%3Fsource_format%3Djpg&h=4ccdcbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預想圖大約係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/49899277_1977660049019024_19245001129066496_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQnA5mug4O8VHKMCoCnZMRxVGgK1tqnFAa1iQ3ki2cfd2un6tfh7jE78sgq-jRK3iL8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=6176571a13f53301c9b0808cdd7e302b&amp;oe=5DE17771\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F49899277_1977660049019024_19245001129066496_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQnA5mug4O8VHKMCoCnZMRxVGgK1tqnFAa1iQ3ki2cfd2un6tfh7jE78sgq-jRK3iL8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D6176571a13f53301c9b0808cdd7e302b%26oe%3D5DE17771&h=7937f8da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知有冇War game 巴打有好介紹，保護度又高，又價錢合理，全黑打CQB 又型仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThanks!"},{"pid":"35f117b1dade5cc26b9e87e993af2e20239ce3ad","tid":1357252,"uid":8005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"我係咪真係開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51253606d1a296ebb9ec83bd7fafac380f40be10","tid":1357252,"uid":40745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"建議唔好貪型，除非你好打得。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 好景後面條街有得買"}]}